# Bookshy ðŸ“š

Bookshy is a simple book management web app built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
It allows users to add books with a title, author, and description, and delete them dynamically.

## Features
- Add new books using a popup form
- Delete books instantly
- Clean and modern UI
- Responsive card layout
- No backend or database required

## Preview
![Bookshy Screenshot](image.png)
<!-- Replace screenshot.png with an actual image of the project -->

## How to Run
1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open `index.html` in your web browser
3. Click the **+** button to add a book

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

